          "description": "Don\u2019t ever go here, my sister is dead because of the mishandling of care with my sister, immunocompromised and put her in a room with another patient and no one had to wear masks, she caught covid plus they left her down there and lied to me about everything with her care, along with Strong hospital in Rochester NY, stay away if you want your loved ones to stay alive",
