          "description": "I am reviewing one doc tor there who is not listed on Google maps.\nHave you ever met a doctor that you knew was going to change your life?\nDr Gustavo Fernandez.\nDr. Fernandez is rare.\nHe resolved issues I was having in one visit that other \"genius\" Doctors could not resolve in 2 years.\nBut he went beyond that. He referred me to other doctors who are equally attentive and responsive.\nNot only does he listen and think outside the box, he also gets back to me as soon as I contact him! Even on the weekends!\nHe was able to discern a problem that I had and was able to refer me to another doctor that helped me get to the bottom of my health issues.\nThe treatments he suggested is successful!\nHe is respectful, kind and professional. If he is your doctor you are fortunate!",
